description:
These files are supplementary files for the article submitted to Pharmaceutics. 

 The .zip archives contain the following files: 

 1) Figures for the Article (normal screenshots and ray-traced screenshots); 

 2) YASARA scenes built for drawing the Figures; 

 3) Results of docking of Geum rivale compounds to the RNA-dependent RNA polymerase of human metapneumovirus; 

 4) Results of docking of nucleotides to the RNA-dependent RNA polymerase of human metapneumovirus; 

 5) results of docking of ellagic acid derivatives to the RNA-dependent RNA polymerase of human metapneumovirus 

 6) results of validation of ellagic acid derivatives on large set of RNA-polymerase PDB files (in two archives, one is short with only 4UCI file, and another one contains larger set of docking complexes obtained using different cell size (30 and 50) and exhaustiveness (8 or 20). The results for cell size of 50 and exhaustiveness of 20 were taken fot the validation table

